{"tid":2245165,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[美國大選] 被忽畧嘅第三、四、五大政黨候選人","createTime":"2020-10-16T04:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T14:38:54.000Z","uid":258706,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a17272154f239aefa287dd3d546385b31a3cc6","tid":2245165,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T04:13:17.000Z","msg":"好多人以為美國大選得兩個候選人可以揀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但其實除咗<span class=\"red\">共和</span>、<span class=\"blue\">民主</span>兩黨，仲有其他未贏過大選嘅大黨參選，分别係 <span class=\"gold\">自由意志黨</span>、<span class=\"green\">綠黨</span>同<span class=\"purple\">聯盟黨</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔少人覺得<span class=\"red\">最大兩黨一樣爛</span>，但礙於覺得投其他大黨都無法令到其他大黨嘅候選人贏，所以決定都係決定投返最大兩黨，形成仲係<span class=\"maroon\">兩黨獨大嘅惡性循環</span><br />\n<br />\n不過，咁又唔代表其他大黨一定冇用咖喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似1996年同2000年咁，多過 8%同2%選民投咗俾其他大黨 (包括<span class=\"green\">綠黨</span>)，左右咗當年選情，嗰2%人甚到令到民主黨最後輸俾共和黨<br />\n<br />\n所以，如果大家識未投票但又唔鍾意Trump嘅美國朋友，<span class=\"orange\">不妨介紹佢認識吓其他大黨嘅候選人</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢投其他大黨嘅一票，分分鐘會令拜登 bye bye咖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參考：<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/2020%E5%B9%B4%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E9%BB%A8%E8%88%87%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E5%80%99%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%BA%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2020%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%2580%2599%25E9%2581%25B8%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25A1%25A8&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU2Fzq3Uwi%2FWN07E9MureYdc%3D&h=d03752d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https: